data.title: Clint Eastwood: Movies, Photos, Videos, News, Biography & Birthday
data.meta_description: Clint Eastwood: Check out the list of all Clint Eastwood movies along with photos, videos, biography and birthday. Also find latest Clint Eastwood news on Times of India.
data.text:
Clint Eastwood's partner Christina Sandera dies at 61

IANS / Jul 20, 2024, 15:54 (IST)

Christina Sandera, partner of actor-director Clint Eastwood, has passed away at 61. The couple maintained a private relationship for the past 10 years. Eastwood expressed his sorrow over her loss. No further details have been disclosed by Warner Brothers.

Today in the past: Interesting things that happened on May 31

etimes.in / May 31, 2024, 06:00 (IST)

May 31st signifies a day of historical significance, marked by events from various domains. From the establishment of essential services to cultural milestones and notable birthdays, this date encapsulates a diverse range of happenings. Noteworthy occurrences include the adoption of symbols of unity, enactment of legislation promoting equality, and significant announcements in popular culture.

Pooja Batra: 'Virasat' changed my life; I want to make a comeback with a project that has a similar impact - Exclusive

etimes.in / Apr 12, 2024, 22:12 (IST)

Former Miss India, Pooja Batra, reveals her journey of transformation and determination. In an interview, she discusses her comeback to India, her desire for substantial roles, and her ambition to make a lasting mark in cinema. Batra's narrative reflects her unwavering commitment to shaping a meaningful career in the industry.

Tom Cruise inks deal with Warner Bros Discovery; to develop and produce original and franchise theatrical films

Reuters / Jan 10, 2024, 08:30 (IST)

Warner Bros Discovery announced a collaboration with Tom Cruise, one of Hollywood's most reliable actors, to create and produce original and franchise theatrical films in 2024. Known for his prominent roles in blockbuster movies like "Top Gun," "The Last Samurai," and the "Mission: Impossible" series, Cruise is set to establish an office on the Warner Bros Discovery lot in Burbank, joining the ranks of stars like Clint Eastwood and Frank Sinatra.

David Soul, Detective Hutch of 1970s hit TV series 'Starsky & Hutch', dies at 80

IANS / Jan 06, 2024, 17:03 (IST)

David Soul, who portrayed Detective Kenneth 'Hutch' Hutchinson in the hit TV series 'Starsky & Hutch', passed away at 80. He was a versatile actor, known for his roles in 'Magnum Force' and 'Salem's Lot'. Soul began his career in the 1960s and gained recognition through his music performances on 'The Merv Griffin Show'. He starred alongside Paul Michael Glaser as Sergeant David Michael Starsky in 'Starsky & Hutch', a beloved cop show of the 70s. Soul was born in Chicago on August 28, 1943, and also appeared in the comedy series 'Here Come the Brides'.

'John Wick' was a 75-year-old man but Keanu Reeves made the character his own

IANS / Jul 19, 2022, 11:15 (IST)

Originally, the character of John Wick was an elderly man of 75 who was supposed to be essayed by the likes of Harrison Ford or Clint Eastwood, but Hollywood star Keanu Reeves took the character and changed it, played it and turned it into one of cinema's most iconic characters, as per the reports.

R Madhavan showers praise on Clint Eastwood and Amitabh Bachchan; reveals he earnestly follows them

etimes.in / Jul 14, 2022, 08:48 (IST)

R Madhavan commands a huge fan following across the nation. While he has inspired many as an actor, he himself is an ardent follower of Clint Eastwood and Amitabh Bachchan.

Clint Eastwood's daughter on growing up with famous dad: He's a down-to-earth person

IANS / Jun 19, 2022, 12:48 (IST)

Hollywood maestro Clint Eastwood's daughter Alison Eastwood has opened up about growing up with her famous dad. In a new interview, the daughter of the legendary actor described her famous father as a "down-to-earth" dad who loves nature and having a beer.

Alphonse Puthren on Mammootty: ‘I think he has more range than Clint Eastwood, Robert De Niro, and Al Pacino’

etimes.in / May 25, 2022, 18:39 (IST)

‘Premam’ director Alphonse Puthren was all excited after watching the Amal Neerad- Mammootty film ‘Bheeshma Parvam’ and said via his official Facebook handle that Mammootty is literally one of the most precious gems of Kerala, Tamil Nadu, India, and even the world. Alphonse Puthren even said that Mammootty has more acting range than the Hollywood A-listers Clint Eastwood, Robert De Niro, and Al Pacino.

Raveena Tandon offers glimpses of her fangirl moments with Al Pacino, Jackie Chan, Amitabh Bachchan and others

TIMESOFINDIA.COM / Sep 30, 2021, 10:03 (IST)

Raveena Tandon enjoys a massive fan following on social media. The actress often shares pictures from her photoshoot, BTS pictures, vacay clicks and more on her Instagram. Recently, she shared a series of photos and offered a glimpse of her fangirl moment with Al Pacino, Jackie Chan, Amitabh Bachchan and others.

Clint Eastwood-starrer 'Cry Macho' to debut in US in October

PTI / Mar 23, 2021, 17:00 (IST)

Veteran actor-director Clint Eastwood's next feature film 'Cry Macho' will release in the US on October 22. The Warner Bros film, which Eastwood has directed and also stars in, will debut both in theatres and on streamer said the reports.
